trans-unit.source: Represents the [<diagnostics>](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/e4ca05d1-1e10-4873-9ef6-75e55851d888) element in the Web.config configuration file.
trans-unit.target: 表示[<诊断>](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/e4ca05d1-1e10-4873-9ef6-75e55851d888) Web.config 配置文件中的元素。

trans-unit.source: The DiagnosticsElement class represents the [\<diagnostics>](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/e4ca05d1-1e10-4873-9ef6-75e55851d888) element in a Web.config file.
trans-unit.target: DiagnosticsElement 类表示[\<诊断&1;>](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/e4ca05d1-1e10-4873-9ef6-75e55851d888) Web.config 文件中的元素。

trans-unit.source: Set the <xref:System.Web.Services.Configuration.DiagnosticsElement.SuppressReturningExceptions%2A> property to true in order to return exceptions to the client for debugging purposes.
trans-unit.target: 设置<xref:System.Web.Services.Configuration.DiagnosticsElement.SuppressReturningExceptions%2A>属性为 true 以返回到客户端的异常，以便进行调试。</xref:System.Web.Services.Configuration.DiagnosticsElement.SuppressReturningExceptions%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.DiagnosticsElement"></xref> class.
Gets or sets a value that indicates whether the service returns exceptions.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置一个值，该值指示服务是否返回异常。

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the service returns exceptions; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>如果该服务返回异常;否则为<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 默认值是<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。
